@node "CONFIG" Configuration


                      @{b}@{u}@{bg shine}Time-UL 1.0 © 1995 Nerve Axis@{ub}@{uu}@{bg back}

Configuration for TIME-UL is decided by the tooltypes within the program
icon.

From here you can set the average cps rates for any of the baud rates.

Set the cps speed for your modem speed to your average upload cps.
This will then ensure accurate results for your modem setup.

Set the DEFRATE to determine which speed is selected when TIME-UL is run.


                            @{"BACK TO MAIN MENU" link "MAIN" 0}
@endnode
